      <hedline>
        <hl1>The End of a Long Life</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Emma Faust Tillman, daughter of former slaves, dies at age 114, four days after becoming world's oldest person (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Emma Faust Tillman, the daughter of former slaves, died Sunday in her sleep at age 114, four days after becoming the world's oldest person. These days, the title changes hands often. Page B1.</p>
      </block>
